              "value": "=Note: The requester {{ $('Restore trigger data').first().json.body['ticket.requester.email'] }} is on the automation blocklist because: {{ $json.matched_reason ? $json.matched_reason : \"no reason provided\" }}. If this requester shouldn't be blocked, please report it to the Operations Department.\n\nAutomation was skipped — please handle this ticket manually.",
